<title>USA: American Travellers acquired by Conseco.</title>
<headline>American Travellers acquired by Conseco.</headline>
<dateline>BENSALEM, Pa. 1996-08-26</dateline>
<text>
<p>American Travellers Corp said Monday it has agreed to be acquired by the Indiana-based insurance holding company Conseco Inc for about $793 million in Conseco stock.</p>
<p>Separately, Conseco said it also agreed to buy Capitol American Financial Corp, which provides cancer insurance and other supplemental health insurance products, for about $650 milion in cash and Conseco stock.</p>
